Professional profile
An enthusiastic and skilled graphic designer who delights in the development process while managing
an effective group. Quick to grasp on new thoughts and ideas, and quick to generate original and creative
solutions to problems. Ability to work independently and achieve results, displaying the high level of drive
needed to reach the tightest deadline. Capacity to multitask and finish tasks under pressure.
Objective
I am currently looking for a new and challenging position that will allow me to utilise my existing skills
and experiences to the fullest and offer the chance for increased responsibility and professional
advancement. In this regard, my main objective is to improve my journalism teaching and research skills
in order to have a greater academic impact and to aid in the growth and advancement of the academic
community.
